item.title: 2018 Wrap-up
item.description: Check Outs PJ FireFox has redeemed itself recently. With better performance it may go back to being my default browser over the security-flawed and processor-heavy Chrome. Something Wicked This Way Comes by Ray Bradbury Mary The ONE Thing by Gary Keller & Jay Papasan Start: Punch Fear in the Face, Escape Average, and Do Work That Matters by Jon Acuff Becoming by Michelle Obama – she narrates the audiobook version Jason Attack of the 50 Foot Blockchain by David Gerard Headspace App Sponsored by: IBM Developer Are you building cloud applications with Java, AI, Machine Learning, Serverless and Containers?
